cus to strategy and taking the company to the next level which is building perry ellis into a global brandto be successful today he said you have to be global because people are increasingly shopping online as well as strongly identifying with the brand they want to buy to meet customers’ changing tastes and shopping habits mr feldenkreis said perry ellis international is adding more brands growing its ecommerce platform and opening up more retail storesin fact the original penguin store at miami international airport is to open today  in concourse d at the end of the day though mr feldenkreis said his biggest accomplishment is identifying with the others working at perry ellis international who include each one of the company’s  associates he said his instincts and vision can be good but the company would not be where it is today without its “good team” mr feldenkreis said it’s much like the legacy of any great sport franchise which he describes as all about the culture passion and execution in particular mr feldenkreis said he attributes his achievement to having his father next to him from the day he started working for the company he sat in his father’s office listening to him and how he conducted business which he said was the greatest education he could have receivedmiami today reporter susan danseyar interviewed mr feldenkreis in his office at perry ellis international headquartersto read the full article and the rest of the miami today issue subscribe to emiami today an exact replica of the printed editionshare this posttweet advertisementrelated articlesrobert rodriguez guiding natcom to produce …juan acosta consolidates viacom productions in new…rene ruiz fashion designer targets hialeah…profile stuart chaseira coleman to run international law firm mcdermott…eric mendelson oversees highflying aerospace…anamarie codina barlick creating acre downtown…martin mendez spearheads it change in health care…profile serge elkinerramona messore develops a very differe